</p>
<p>To use the cache service, add <code>if ($cache-&gt;contains($key))</code>. In this case,
just set <code>$funFact = $cache-&gt;fetch($key);</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="a1f40a624c">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-55" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
